{"tid":2134519,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（2015年舊聞） 李登輝預言2020年中美出現大戰","createTime":"2020-07-31T18:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T15:17:22.000Z","uid":362199,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"501de798ffdc9a9600014e6cad209f4abe5ae793","tid":2134519,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T18:41:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/gb/2015/02/03/a1174400.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fgb%2F2015%2F02%2F03%2Fa1174400.html&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOVMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=8aeb8ab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/gb/2015/02/03/a1174400.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iS0X53c87Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiS0X53c87Q4&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOVMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=75a89fd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iS0X53c87Q4</a><br />\n<br />\n前總統李登輝：&ldquo;盡量講話講少一點，重點抓住，這樣一來，我看，才不用再吃(降高血壓)藥。&rdquo;<br />\n奉勸台北市長柯文哲，講話前得先三思，前總統李登輝，為柯文哲爭議&ldquo;殖民說&rdquo;緩頰，但對於柯文哲的&ldquo;兩國一制&rdquo;新論調，倒是非常認同。<br />\n前總統李登輝：&ldquo;兩個國家，只有一種制度，就是自由、民主、法治、人權，這我是很同意啦。現在最重要的問題是，中國沒有自由，也沒有宗教自由。&rdquo;<br />\n提出自己博覽群書的見解，李登輝認為，2020年左右，美日和中共，可能因釣魚台发生沖突，世界局勢變動導致中國民主化，台灣在那之後，才有可能獨立自主。"},{"pid":"06661fb1c2cc2b4d727ffabe4fc07309ff89ca05","tid":2134519,"uid":343268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T22:16:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c41fc3e646345c7c31d9801e363e9465cd428b11","tid":2134519,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T00:13:59.000Z","msg":"好撚通透 連柯都睇穿埋"},{"pid":"ede650a0b9fd08ee77ba94fd04e95a84a78545e0","tid":2134519,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06661fb1c2cc2b4d727ffabe4fc07309ff89ca05","tid":2134519,"uid":343268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T22:16:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01